      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through a variable M differential lock. The chassis has been enhanced with a documented rear subframe reinforcement kit, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and rod bearing replacement. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance characteristic of the E46 platform. A mechanically sound driver's car ready for the apex.",
